data: {"tool_call_id": "call_gQbW5mzb8E7QjC3VL1Vef8ST", "tool_name": "web_search", "result": "# Search Results for: 2012 Daewoo Lacetti pre purchase inspection checklist\n\nFound 5 results:\n\n## 1. 2012 DAEWOO Lacetti Recalls, Complaints and Investigations - The Center for Auto Safety\n**URL:** https://www.autosafety.org/vehicle-safety-check/2012-daewoo-lacetti/\nFebruary 8, 2021 - 2012 DAEWOO Lacetti is it safe? Read all complaints, recalls and other safety issues for 2012 DAEWOO Lacetti\n\n## 2. Car Inspection Checklist for Buyers: Complete Pre\u2011Purchase - The Rocky Mountain Collegian\n**URL:** https://collegian.com/sponsored/2026/01/car-inspection-checklist-for-buyers-a-complete-guide/\n3 weeks ago - Before checking tires or fluids, unlock the past. Use https://epicvin.com/license-plate-lookup/new-jersey to run a vehicle history report. It reveals accidents, salvage titles, and ownership changes. That\u2019s where a proper inspection checklist begins.\n\n## 3. How to Perform a Used-Car Inspection | Auto Care Plus\n**URL:** https://www.autocareplus.com/lp/vehicle-pre-purchase-inspection-checklist/\nAugust 12, 2025 - How to Perform a Used-Car Inspection Avoid the most common, costly mistakes before you purchase that vehicle. NOTE: This checklist is a courtesy to help people shopping for used vehicles. IT IS NOT A SUBSTITUTE FOR AN INSPECTION BY A QUALIFIED TECHNICIAN. There are many issues that are difficult to find without a trained eye ...\n\n## 4. Pre-Purchase Car Inspection Checklist By VLX\n**URL:** https://visualogyx.com/pre-purchase-inspection-checklist/\nAugust 16, 2025 - These could range from engine troubles and transmission wear to signs of previous accidents or flood damage that have been concealed . A comprehensive inspection can uncover these hidden defects, ensuring that the buyer is not misled by appearances ...\n\n## 5. Vehicle Pre-Purchase Inspection Checklist | 24 Auto Group\n**URL:** https://www.24autogroup.com/vehicle-pre-purchase-inspection-checklist.htm\nWhen you're buying a new-to-you car, you want to feel confident it's the right choice for you. Our team at 24 Auto Group wants to help you do exactly that! An inspection before buying is vital to confirm what you're getting, and we created this vehicle pre-purchase inspection checklist to help you.\n"}

